headline: 10,000 Runners Hit the Streets for Sands China Macao International 10K
summary: The 2025 Sands China Macao International 10K welcomed around 10,000 runners from 40 countries and regions March 16, who crossed the finish line after completing either the 10K race or the Fun Run.
